latestIgtvVideos.caption:
'Back' to the same old grind 🙁
(Pun intended lmao)

There are times when I feel like my Instagram is misleading, even a little contrary to who I am as a person.🙄 It's definitely not intentional but is something I've come to realise of late. 😳

While it is not inaccurate to say that I LOVE to wear Indian 🥻 and I think that there is no such thing as too much bling ✨ but at the same time there's more to me than aesthetic side profiles 😔

It's really easy to get caught up with pushing the best version of yourself out on the internet and sometimes I forget that most of my viewers don't know who I really am.🤷🏻‍♀️ I've always been self conscious of my smile and as a result I've been very careful with the content I put up.

So, in order to switch things up, here's a little snippet of me goofing around with one of my favourite people on the planet. This is me, my smile is a tad bit too wide and my voice may not be what you've imagined it to be but hey, at least now you know 😏😉
